<topic id='class_offer_of_admission.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Class: OFFER OF ADMISSION - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>

  <p>
This records each 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_offer_of_admission">OFFER OF ADMISSION</xref>
 made to a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 on the 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_elective_admission_list">ELECTIVE ADMISSION LIST</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
When the 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 accepts an 
    <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_offered_for_admission_date">OFFERED FOR ADMISSION DATE</xref>
, it is this offered date that the 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 is expected to attend and be admitted.  </p>
  <p>
      <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_admission_offer_outcome">ADMISSION OFFER OUTCOME</xref>
 records whether or not the 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 was admitted and the circumstances that applied.  </p>

</body>
